@shinya321 If you're using "--mode=quantize" on the latest master commit of tensorflow, I found that there is a bug in the code that produces a KeyError at

tensorflow/tensorflow/tools/quantization/quantize_graph.py

Line 490 in 9590c4c

if self.already_visited[current_node.name]:

That line should be changed from:

if self.already_visited[current_node.name]:

to:

if current_node.name in self.already_visited and self.already_visited[current_node.name]:
